end-user means a final consumer of or subscriber to a public telecommunications service, including a service supplier other than a supplier of public telecommunications services; essential facilities means facilities of a public telecommunications network or service that: 


(a) 	are exclusively or predominantly provided by a single or limited number of suppliers; and 


